### ================================================================================
### 🎵 拍卖管理模块接口测试
### ================================================================================
### 功能：创建拍卖、查询拍卖、开始拍卖、取消拍卖等
### 依赖：需要商家Token和商品ID（auth + products模块）
### 权限：商家/管理员
### ================================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@merchantToken = {{merchantToken}}
@productId = {{productId}}
@auctionId = {{auctionId}}

### ================================================================================
### 🆕 创建拍卖活动
### ================================================================================

### 1.1 创建标准拍卖活动
POST {{baseUrl}}/auctions
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": {{productId}},
  "title": "iPhone 15 Pro Max 新机拍卖",
  "startPrice": 8799.00,
  "bidIncrement": 100.00,
  "maxPrice": 15000.00,
  "delaySeconds": 15,
  "startTime": "2026-06-08T10:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-06-08T12:00:00"
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        var body = JSON.parse(response.body);
        if (body.data && body.data.id) {
            client.global.set("auctionId", body.data.id);
            client.log("✅ 拍卖活动创建成功");
            client.log("🎵 拍卖ID: " + body.data.id);
            client.log("📦 商品ID: " + body.data.productId);
            client.log("💰 起拍价: " + body.data.startPrice);
            client.log("⏰ 开始时间: " + body.data.startTime);
            client.log("⏰ 结束时间: " + body.data.endTime);
        }
    } else {
        client.log("❌ 拍卖活动创建失败: " + response.body);
    }
%}

### 1.2 创建奢侈品拍卖
POST {{baseUrl}}/auctions
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 2,
  "title": "LV限量版手提包拍卖",
  "startPrice": 10000.00,
  "bidIncrement": 500.00,
  "maxPrice": 25000.00,
  "delaySeconds": 10,
  "startTime": "2026-06-08T14:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-06-08T16:00:00"
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 200) {
        client.log("✅ 奢侈品拍卖创建成功");
    }
%}

### 1.3 创建艺术品拍卖
POST {{baseUrl}}/auctions
Authorization: Bearer {{merchantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 3,
  "title": "名家山水画拍卖",
  "startPrice": 30000.00,
  "bidIncrement": 1000.00,
  "maxPrice": 80000.00,
  "delaySeconds": 20,
  "startTime": "2026-06-08T18:00:00",
